description: Edamame beans add extra goodness and texture to this guacamole style dip.

name: Edamame & Avocado Dip with Carrot Sticks Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 3 large carrots, peeled and sliced into batons

recipeInstructions.text: In a pan of boiling water, blanch the edamame for 2 minutes and drain.
Place the edamame, avocados, garlic, oil, lime juice and coriander in a food processor and pulse to a chunky dip consistency.
Dice the jalapenos and stir through. Serve the dip in a bowl surrounded by carrot sticks.
